list.name: Changes
list.comment:
Full Chess functionality with selected squares being controlled by WASD keys.
Selecting a piece is LEFT_CLICK. Moving to a square is RIGHT_CLICK.
Known bugs and or improvements: Player must always have an item in their hand to acknowledge right clicks Players can get teleported to chess board without consent Players dont get teleported back to original position upon end of game. The plugin can only be used in the world it is developed in. Previous selected squares is slightly incorrect
